Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用魔法了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米拉克Rainbow
